🧠 SkillForge AI

Intelligent Skill Gap Analyzer & Career Roadmap Generator

SkillForge AI is a modern, single-page Web Application designed to analyze a user's current skill set against the industry demands of top tech careers (like Data Science, AI Engineering, and Software Engineering).

🚀 Features

Skill Gap Analyzer: Compares user skills with target role requirements to calculate a match score.

Dynamic Roadmaps: Automatically generates a step-by-step learning path to acquire missing skills.

3D Visualizations: Built with Three.js to provide an immersive neural-network aesthetic.

Interactive Radar Charts: Uses Chart.js to visually map skill competencies.

AI Chatbot Mentor: A simulated chat interface to provide context-aware career advice.

No Backend Required: State is preserved seamlessly in the browser using localStorage.

🛠️ Technology Stack

Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6)

Styling: Tailwind CSS (via CDN)

3D Engine: Three.js

Data Visualization: Chart.js

Icons: FontAwesome

🌐 How to Deploy on Netlify (Drag and Drop)

Create a folder on your desktop called SkillForge.

Move index.html and README.md into this folder.

Go to Netlify Drop.

Drag and drop your SkillForge folder into the upload box on their website.

Your site is now live! Netlify will provide you with a public URL you can share immediately.